# tfe_team_member

Add or remove a user from a team.

~> **NOTE** on managing team memberships: Terraform currently provides four resources for managing team memberships. The [tfe_team_organization_member](team_organization_member.html) and [tfe_team_organization_members](team_organization_members.html) resources are the preferred way. The [tfe_team_member](team_member.html) resource can be used multiple times as it manages the team membership for a single user. The [tfe_team_members](team_members.html) resource, on the other hand, is used to manage all team memberships for a specific team and can only be used once. All four resources cannot be used for the same team simultaneously.

